录剩余时长和是否暂停:\r\n```\r\nid int\r\n...\r\npaused bool\r\ntime_remain int\r\n```\r\n\r\n然后再开一个定时任务每五分钟把没有暂停的用户时间-5\r\n\r\n求教各位老哥有没有更优雅的方法", "content_rendered": "<p>正在设计一个类似雷神/Golink 的加速器系统，没想好怎么实现暂停时长</p>\n<p>目前的想法是有一个用户表记录剩余时长和是否暂停:</p>\n<pre><code>id int\n...\npaused bool\ntime_remain int\n</code></pre>\n<p>然后再开一个定时任务每五分钟把没有暂停的用户时间-5</p>\n<p>求教各位老哥有没有更优雅的方法</p>\n", "last_modified": 1707619897, "replies": 23, "id": 1015307}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/d67d/8ab4/39_large.png?m=1651385965", "name": "android", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/d67d/8ab4/39_normal.png?m=1651385965", "title": "Android", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/android", "topics": 11165, "footer": "", "header": "来自 <a href=\"/go/google\">Google</a> 的开放源代码智能手机平台。", "title_alternative": "Android", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/d67d/8ab4/39_mini.png?m=1651385965", "stars": 5736, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 39, "parent_node_name": "hardware"}, "member": {"id": 352727, "username": "Sindo", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/Sindo", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/03dc/926d/352727_mini.png?m=1607877320", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/03dc/926d/352727_normal.png?m=1607877320", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/03dc/926d/352727_large.png?m=1607877320", "created": 1538100437, "last_modified": 1607877320}, "last_reply_by": "Sindo", "last_touched": 1707667626, "title": "安卓输入法的多语言切换怎么才能更丝滑一点？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1015349", "created": 1707652507, "deleted": 0, "content": "我输入日语和泰语时用 Gboard （日语泰语词库全，语言识别准确）\r\n我输入中文用搜狗/讯飞/百度等国产输入法（ Gboard 的中文词库真的太少了）\r\n\r\n- Gboard→国产输入法：直接点小地球即可，很方便\r\n- 国产输入法→Gboard：小地球没了，必须得进系统设置里面更改输入法，非常繁琐，这是问题所在。\r\n\r\n想寻找一款支持快速切换到 Gboard 的中文输入法，各位有没有什么推荐呢？", "content_rendered": "<p>我输入日语和泰语时用 Gboard （日语泰语词库全，语言识别准确）\n我输入中文用搜狗/讯飞/百度等国产输入法（ Gboard 的中文词库真的太少了）</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Gboard→国产输入法：直接点小地球即可，很方便</li>\n<li>国产输入法→Gboard：小地球没了，必须得进系统设置里面更改输入法，非常繁琐，这是问题所在。</li>\n</ul>\n<p>想寻找一款支持快速切换到 Gboard 的中文输入法，各位有没有什么推荐呢？</p>\n", "last_modified": 1707652507, "replies": 18, "id": 1015349}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_large.png?m=1650095340", "name": "qna", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_normal.png?m=1650095340", "title": "问与答", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna", "topics": 215110, "footer": "", "header": "一个更好的世界需要你持续地提出好问题。", "title_alternative": "Questions and Answers", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1650095340", "stars": 4088, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 12, "parent_node_name": "v2ex"}, "member": {"id": 563568, "username": "szj", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/szj", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/48fbe0807c00f1269068991509c8c819?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/48fbe0807c00f1269068991509c8c819?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/48fbe0807c00f1269068991509c8c819?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1638096277, "last_modified": 1638097555}, "last_reply_by": "zhangH258", "last_touched": 1707649385, "title": "养老保险最低一千", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1015333", "created": 1707640809, "deleted": 0, "content": "父母查了查，一直都是最低档，2017 年以前都是 100 ，2018 2019 2020 三年 200 2021 年 300 2022 年 2023 年 500 ，今年  1000 最低档！诸位这么说？？？", "content_rendered": "父母查了查，一直都是最低档，2017 年以前都是 100 ，2018 2019 2020 三年 200 2021 年 300 2022 年 2023 年 500 ，今年  1000 最低档！诸位这么说？？？", "last_modified": 1707640809, "replies": 17, "id": 1015333}]